</span></span></span><![endif]><b style=3D'mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><sp=
an
lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB'>Poor reputation</span></b><s=
pan
lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB'> &#8211; some alien races ca=
n become
quite concerned if your empire has a poor reputation, lowering your approval
rating.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB'>S=
trive to
maintain a high approval rating by ensuring your colonies have high develop=
ment
levels. This is achieved by securing the trade routes to and from your colo=
nies
so that luxury resources can safely reach them.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB'>A=
lso, be
careful not to raise taxes too high &#8211; it&#8217;s usually a good idea =
to
allow colony taxes to be automatically controlled (default setting in Game
Options).<o:p></o:p></span></p>

